metadata.name: HOME #1
metadata.description:
This NFT is a pathway into my world. Welcome and close the door behind you. Milana and I came together to create a song that reflects
our innermost urges, testing temptation in the most seductive of ways. Desires are sometimes uncontrollable, and we hope this song unleashes every one of them.


Utility:

-Free use of the song in any shape or form.
-50% discount on the next Max Pretends NFT drop.
-50% discount on the “Home” music video NFT drop.
-Six album covers are stamped with a 
"max pretends" logo—the holders of these 6 assets will be invited to attend a max pretends songwriting camp, taking place in the heart of Brooklyn, NY during summer 2023.
